OL,3,CFamily of Gemma Simpson 'terrified'
OL,4,Cafter killer recommended for open
OL,5,Cprison
OL,7,FThe family of a woman, who was
OL,8,Fbrutally killed and dismembered by a
OL,9,Ftaxi driver in Harrogate, have said
OL,10,Fthey feel "terrified" after the Parole
OL,11,FBoard recommended he is moved to an
OL,12,Fopen prison.
OL,14,FMartin Bell, 55, was given a life
OL,15,Fsentence at Leeds Crown Court in 2014
OL,16,Fand ordered to serve a minimum of 12
OL,17,Fyears in prison for the manslaughter
OL,18,Fof Gemma Simpson, who disappeared in
OL,19,FMay 2000.
