OL,3,CFamily of Gemma Simpson 'terrified'
OL,4,Cafter killer recommended for open
OL,5,Cprison
OL,7,F"After his confession, he tried to
OL,8,Fkeep her remains from us, making us
OL,9,Fwait four months before she came home
OL,10,Fand the truth was discovered.
OL,12,F"We want justice for Gemma and, at
OL,13,Fpresent, we feel she is not getting
OL,14,Fjustice or even considered.
OL,16,F"His feelings and rights seem more
OL,17,Fimportant than Gemma's or ours."
