OL,7,FMs Simpson and Ms Carrack said: "We
OL,8,Fare terrified for ourselves and
OL,9,Fothers. As the judge said in court he
OL,10,Fis at high-risk of re-offending. What
OL,11,Freassurances can we be given that he
OL,12,Fwon't re-offend?"
OL,14,FMiss Simpson was 23 when taxi driver
OL,15,FBell attacked her with a knife and a
OL,16,Fhammer at his flat in Harrogate in
OL,17,F2000.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
