OL,7,FHe then dismembered her body and
OL,8,Fburied it at Brimham Rocks in North
OL,9,FYorkshire, where it lay undiscovered
OL,10,Funtil he handed himself in to police
OL,11,Fin 2014.
OL,13,FHe later pleaded guilty to
OL,14,Fmanslaughter on the grounds of
OL,15,Fdiminished responsibility after being
OL,16,Fdiagnosed with schizophrenia.
