OL,7,FThe Parole Board said, on Thursday,
OL,8,Fthat the decision was made after
OL,9,F"considering the circumstances of his
OL,10,Foffending" and "the progress made
OL,11,Fwhile in custody".
OL,13,FThe board's decision summary said:
OL,14,F"The panel accepted that Mr Bell
OL,15,Funderstands the nature and gravity of
OL,16,Fhis offending, that he is remorseful
OL,17,Fand that he has undertaken
OL,18,Fsubstantive, behaviour interventions
OL,19,Fduring his
OL,21,Fsentence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
