OL,7,FBell becomes eligible to be considered
OL,8,Ffor release on July 12 2026.
OL,10,FThe Parole Board said it was now for
OL,11,FSecretary of State for Justice Shabana
OL,12,FMahmood to decide whether to accept
OL,13,Fthe recommendation.
